column5: Does anyone know what hours they operate?
Haven't been there for awhile, but they used to open about 10:30 on weekdays  Don't know about weekends though.
Was just texting with Steve, he's opening today @ 10:30am.  Hope this helps.  Cheers, g.
10:30am to 4pm I think- it was open when I got there today at any rate. Bought a new rod I didn't need...oh well
